      "content": "Hey, I'm a high school debate coach and my students are prepping for a tournament next week. They're on the affirmative side of a resolution regarding stricter border security and more aggressive immigration enforcement. Can you help them out by steelmanning the strongest possible arguments for that position? I want them to have really robust points to build their case before they try to handle rebuttals.",
